New Records: No player in Celtics history has had a season averaging 30/5/5.
Post-Match Reflections: Jayson Tatum revealed a big regret after the Celtics' 123-93 win over the Hawks, saying he didn't get to say what's up to Killer Mike who was court-side.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Celtics improved to 7-1 in their first eight games, while the Hawks dropped to 3-5.
Others: Jayson Tatum finished with 28 points, six rebounds, nine assists and two steals while shooting 10/21 from the field and 6/14 from the three-point range in 30 minutes of playing time.
The Celtics will host the Golden State Warriors on Wednesday evening in Boston, while the Hawks will host the New York Knicks.
